  * Patch changes:
    + debian-changes -- removed in favor of pigeonhole.patch
    + dovecot_name.patch -- fixed manually
    + exampledir.patch -- quilt refreshed
    + lda-2.3.1+.patch -- removed, fixed by upstream
    + murmur3-big-endian.patch -- removed, fixed by upstream
    + split-protocols.patch -- quilt refreshed
  * Add Docker.build script for easier (re)building.
