dovecot (1:2.3.1-0osso1) xenial; urgency=medium

  * Updated to upstream dovecot-2.3.1.tar.gz.
  * Imported most of the config from the dovecot_2.3.1-2.debian.tar.xz
    (from https://launchpad.net/debian/+source/dovecot/1:2.3.1-2#).
  * Skipped a few changes to rules/compat/packaging. That's for a later day.
  * Add LDA fix so we can accept bounces again. Fixes:
    "status=bounced (command line usage error. Command output: lda: Fatal:
    Invalid -f parameter: Missing domain )"

